---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8" />
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
	<meta name="description" content="bae - Your music as easy as streaming. Metadata-driven import from MusicBrainz and Discogs, pregap-accurate playback, encrypted storage." />
	<title>bae - Your music as easy as streaming</title>
	<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
	<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
	<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Instrument+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&family=DM+Serif+Display&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
	<div class="noise"></div>

	<nav>
		<a href="/" class="logo"><img src="/sheep.png" alt="" class="logo-icon" />bae</a>
		<div class="nav-links">
			<a href="/getting-started/installation">Docs</a>
			<a href="https://github.com/bae-fm/bae" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
		</div>
	</nav>

	<main>
		<section class="hero">
			<div class="hero-content">
				<h1>Your music<br/><span class="accent">as easy as streaming</span></h1>
				<p class="tagline">Scale your collection effortlessly and listen anywhere — without handing your music to someone else.</p>
				<div class="cta-group">
					<a href="https://github.com/bae-fm/bae/releases/latest/download/bae.dmg" class="btn primary">
						<svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
							<path d="M12 2C6.477 2 2 6.477 2 12c0 4.42 2.865 8.166 6.839 9.489.5.092.682-.217.682-.482 0-.237-.008-.866-.013-1.7-2.782.604-3.369-1.34-3.369-1.34-.454-1.156-1.11-1.463-1.11-1.463-.908-.62.069-.608.069-.608 1.003.07 1.531 1.03 1.531 1.03.892 1.529 2.341 1.087 2.91.831.092-.646.35-1.086.636-1.336-2.22-.253-4.555-1.11-4.555-4.943 0-1.091.39-1.984 1.029-2.683-.103-.253-.446-1.27.098-2.647 0 0 .84-.269 2.75 1.025A9.578 9.578 0 0112 6.836c.85.004 1.705.114 2.504.336 1.909-1.294 2.747-1.025 2.747-1.025.546 1.377.203 2.394.1 2.647.64.699 1.028 1.592 1.028 2.683 0 3.842-2.339 4.687-4.566 4.935.359.309.678.919.678 1.852 0 1.336-.012 2.415-.012 2.743 0 .267.18.578.688.48C19.138 20.163 22 16.418 22 12c0-5.523-4.477-10-10-10z"/>
						</svg>
						Download for macOS
					</a>
					<a href="/getting-started/installation" class="btn secondary">Read the docs</a>
				</div>
				<p class="platform-note">Windows & Linux coming soon</p>
			</div>
			<div class="hero-visual">
				<img
					src="/screenshots/library-grid.png"
					alt="bae music library showing album grid view"
					class="app-screenshot"
					onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';"
				/>
				<div class="window-frame" style="display: none;">
					<div class="window-controls">
						<span></span><span></span><span></span>
					</div>
					<div class="window-content">
						<div class="placeholder-app">
							<div class="sidebar">
								<div class="sidebar-item active"></div>
								<div class="sidebar-item"></div>
								<div class="sidebar-item"></div>
								<div class="sidebar-item"></div>
							</div>
							<div class="content-area">
								<div class="album-grid">
									<div class="album"></div>
									<div class="album"></div>
									<div class="album"></div>
									<div class="album"></div>
									<div class="album"></div>
									<div class="album"></div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="concepts">
			<div class="concept">
				<h2>Your music, your storage</h2>
				<p>Your library lives on your machine by default. No cloud required, no account, no subscription. When you're ready to scale, bae supports S3-compatible storage (AWS, Backblaze B2, etc.) with encryption — files are encrypted before they leave your machine.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="concept">
				<h2>Rich collecting</h2>
				<p>bae understands <em>releases</em>, not just files. Point it at a folder, search MusicBrainz or Discogs for the release, and bae pulls in album art, credits, label, catalog number, barcode — everything the database knows about that pressing.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="concept">
				<h2>Authentic playback</h2>
				<p>Albums play back the way they were meant to be heard. CUE/FLAC pregaps are preserved — the silence, the hidden intro, the crossfade the artist intended. Single-file albums stream as individual tracks without being split.</p>
				<p class="coming-soon">Coming soon: LP mode pauses at side breaks so you can "flip the record" and continue.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="concept">
				<h2>Stream anywhere</h2>
				<p>bae runs a Subsonic API server on your machine. Connect any Subsonic-compatible client to stream your library wherever you are.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="concept">
				<h2>Open source</h2>
				<p>Built with Rust and Dioxus. MIT licensed. <a href="https://github.com/bae-fm/bae" target="_blank">Contribute on GitHub</a>.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="mission">
			<p>Music ownership shouldn't be complicated. bae exists to make owning, organizing, and playing your own music as straightforward as streaming.</p>
		</section>

		<section class="download-cta">
			<h2>Try bae</h2>
			<p>Free, open source, no account required.</p>
			<a href="https://github.com/bae-fm/bae/releases/latest/download/bae.dmg" class="btn primary large">
				Download for macOS
			</a>
		</section>
	</main>

	<footer>
		<div class="footer-content">
			<span class="footer-logo">bae</span>
			<div class="footer-links">
				<a href="/getting-started/installation">Docs</a>
				<a href="https://github.com/bae-fm/bae" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
				<a href="https://github.com/bae-fm/bae/releases" target="_blank">Releases</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</footer>
</body>
</html>

<style>
	* {
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0;
		box-sizing: border-box;
	}

	:root {
		--bg: #0a0a0c;
		--bg-subtle: #111114;
		--text: #e8e8ed;
		--text-muted: #8b8b96;
		--accent: #a855f7;
		--accent-dim: #7c3aed;
		--border: #1f1f24;
	}

	html {
		font-family: 'Instrument Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
		background: var(--bg);
		color: var(--text);
		scroll-behavior: smooth;
	}

	body {
		min-height: 100vh;
		position: relative;
		overflow-x: hidden;
	}

	.noise {
		position: fixed;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		pointer-events: none;
		opacity: 0.03;
		background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
		z-index: 1000;
	}

	nav {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: center;
		padding: 1.5rem 3rem;
		max-width: 1400px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.logo {
		font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
		font-size: 1.85rem;
		color: var(--text);
		text-decoration: none;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.4rem;
	}

	.logo-icon {
		width: 120px;
		height: 120px;
		margin: -30px -20px -30px -15px;
	}

	.nav-links {
		display: flex;
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.nav-links a {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		text-decoration: none;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		transition: color 0.2s;
	}

	.nav-links a:hover {
		color: var(--text);
	}

	main {
		max-width: 1400px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 3rem;
	}

	/* Hero */

	.hero {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 4rem;
		align-items: center;
		min-height: 80vh;
		padding: 4rem 0;
	}

	h1 {
		font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
		font-size: 3.5rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		line-height: 1.15;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	h1 .accent {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent) 0%, #ec4899 100%);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
	}

	.tagline {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		max-width: 440px;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.cta-group {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.btn {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		padding: 0.875rem 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 500;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		transition: all 0.2s;
	}

	.btn.primary {
		background: var(--accent);
		color: white;
	}

	.btn.primary:hover {
		background: var(--accent-dim);
		transform: translateY(-1px);
	}

	.btn.secondary {
		background: var(--bg-subtle);
		color: var(--text);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
	}

	.btn.secondary:hover {
		background: var(--border);
	}

	.btn.large {
		padding: 1rem 2rem;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}

	.platform-note {
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}

	.hero-visual {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.app-screenshot {
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 600px;
		border-radius: 12px;
		box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
	}

	.window-frame {
		background: var(--bg-subtle);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: 12px;
		overflow: hidden;
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 500px;
		box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
	}

	.window-controls {
		display: flex;
		gap: 8px;
		padding: 12px 16px;
		background: var(--border);
	}

	.window-controls span {
		width: 12px;
		height: 12px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: #3f3f46;
	}

	.window-content {
		padding: 0;
	}

	.placeholder-app {
		display: flex;
		height: 300px;
	}

	.sidebar {
		width: 60px;
		background: #18181b;
		padding: 12px;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 8px;
	}

	.sidebar-item {
		width: 36px;
		height: 36px;
		border-radius: 8px;
		background: #27272a;
	}

	.sidebar-item.active {
		background: var(--accent-dim);
	}

	.content-area {
		flex: 1;
		padding: 16px;
		background: var(--bg);
	}

	.album-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 12px;
	}

	.album {
		aspect-ratio: 1;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #27272a 0%, #18181b 100%);
		border-radius: 6px;
	}

	.album:nth-child(1) { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed 0%, #4c1d95 100%); }
	.album:nth-child(2) { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ec4899 0%, #be185d 100%); }
	.album:nth-child(3) { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #b45309 100%); }
	.album:nth-child(4) { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #047857 100%); }
	.album:nth-child(5) { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #1d4ed8 100%); }

	/* Mission */

	.mission {
		max-width: 700px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 4rem 0 6rem;
		text-align: center;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
	}

	.mission p {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-style: italic;
	}

	/* Concept sections */

	.concepts {
		padding: 2rem 0 4rem;
	}

	.concept {
		max-width: 700px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 3rem 0;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
	}

	.concept h2 {
		font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.concept p {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	.concept p:last-child {
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	.concept a {
		color: var(--accent);
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	.concept a:hover {
		text-decoration: underline;
	}

	.coming-soon {
		font-size: 0.9rem !important;
		opacity: 0.7;
		font-style: italic;
	}

	/* Download CTA */

	.download-cta {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 6rem 0;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
	}

	.download-cta h2 {
		font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.download-cta p {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	/* Footer */

	footer {
		border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
		padding: 2rem 3rem;
	}

	.footer-content {
		max-width: 1400px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.footer-logo {
		font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}

	.footer-links {
		display: flex;
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.footer-links a {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		text-decoration: none;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		transition: color 0.2s;
	}

	.footer-links a:hover {
		color: var(--text);
	}

	/* Responsive */

	@media (max-width: 1024px) {
		.hero {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			text-align: center;
			min-height: auto;
		}

		h1 {
			font-size: 2.75rem;
		}

		.tagline {
			max-width: none;
		}

		.cta-group {
			justify-content: center;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		nav, main, footer {
			padding-left: 1.5rem;
			padding-right: 1.5rem;
		}

		h1 {
			font-size: 2.25rem;
		}

		.cta-group {
			flex-direction: column;
		}

		.concept {
			padding: 2rem 0;
		}
	}
</style>
